            <div class="orbit" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <article class="workflow-screen active" id="screen-order" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-order">
              <span class="screen-tag">Order captured</span>
              <h3>Fast billing without hunting through menus.</h3>
              <p>Cashiers search, modify, split, and settle orders from a focused register designed for busy service periods.</p>
              <div class="screen-metrics">
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>POS</strong><span>Counter orders</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>QR</strong><span>Guest ordering</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Tables</strong><span>Dine-in mapping</span></div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="workflow-screen" id="screen-kitchen" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-kitchen" hidden>
              <span class="screen-tag">Kitchen notified</span>
              <h3>Every item reaches the right preparation queue.</h3>
              <p>Digital tickets carry table, modifier, and timing details so the kitchen can prioritize work without paper slips or repeated calls.</p>
              <div class="screen-metrics">
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Live</strong><span>Ticket status</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Timed</strong><span>Delay alerts</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Clear</strong><span>Item modifiers</span></div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="workflow-screen" id="screen-stock" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-stock" hidden>
              <span class="screen-tag">Records updated</span>
              <h3>Recipes reduce stock as dishes are sold.</h3>
              <p>Ingredient usage, low-stock warnings, and customer history update behind the scenes, keeping records closer to reality.</p>
              <div class="screen-metrics">
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Gram</strong><span>Recipe tracking</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>Low</strong><span>Stock warnings</span></div>
                <div class="screen-metric"><strong>CRM</strong><span>Visit history</span></div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="workflow-screen" id="screen-settle" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-settle" hidden>
              <span class="screen-tag">Shift reconciled</span>
              <h3>Payments, invoices, and reports stay connected.</h3>
